        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>Some 91/92/93/9400 Models built between September 1, 1996 and July 3, 1998 may exhibit
                    harsh/erratic clutch engagement. This condition can be corrected by replacing the clutch bellcrank
                    relay lever, clutch release shaft lever and the lower control rod (
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f9811021">Figure 1</hotlnk>).
                </para>
                <figure id="f9811021" figsize="pg-wide">
                    <graphic filename="../tsifigures/G9811021.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 1. Replace Clutch Bellcrank Relay Lever, Clutch Release Shaft Lever, and Lower
                        Control Rod
                    </caption>
                </figure>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
